<td><FONT SIZE="1" FACE="Verdana, Arial" COLOR="#2f2f4f">Originally posted by Shohanna Curesurtales on 04-11-2001 11:55 PM<BR></FONT>
<TEXTAREA NAME="EditedMessage" ROWS=10 COLS=45 WRAP="VIRTUAL">I think I actually end up spamming my group.. But no one has told me to stop.. or if they didn't like it left the group..  My roleplay is durring my entire time I am playing Sho..
When she casts a heal, a buff, any spell.. I set up that she says something about Brell sirillis.. (sp)  hehe yes I know I should know how to spell it.. but I just use Brell.

like, when I sup heal..
/g Shohanna feels that her prayer is heard for <player name>. 
and for complete heal
/em shohanna screams as the power rushes thru her viens.
/g There be healing going on here!! 11 seconds
/g and I do mean HEALING GOING ON!!! 5 seconds.
and say if they need a top off of heal, 
/point to target.
/g you get the baby heal!
for group heal I have a special one.
shohanna bows her head in preparation of her god's touch.
/g Gather round for a special heal from Brell.


My buff line match what the "return" message is when you cast on someone..
/g May this Symbol of Pinzarn keep you from harm. 
/g I bless thee <target>.
/g May you always be Valorous
/g May the evil stay away from you with this blessing..
/g May the gods bless you.. and keep you away from deaths door..

Things like that.. All my spells say something, tho as I sit here, I can't remember the rest of them!! hehe
But like if she is OOm, I hit my /med hot key that says 
shohanna falls to the ground.
/g the power has left me for now..

I get lots of comments, that they enjoy it, and know what to expect.. 

My stun lines don't have a comment.. None are needed.. I don't have Offensive spells up yet.. I been too busy healing!

Mostly because I like to have 2 clerics and 3 tanks and 1 druid/shaman/bard/enchanter in group and we play "dueling" clerics..
Where Each tank pulls something in, and starts beating it.. first one needs a heal, One cleric heals, then the next the next cleric heals..  Both clerics play main healer. the EXP is awesome.. and it also adds to the fun of "trains"

So there isn't time to do the offensive spells, unless me chanter is in need, and then I have my hot key just for the chanter..
and it's cute
/target chanter name
/g OMG BRELL screamed that you WILL NOT DIE!!!
and it auto casts gheal, and then pauses and 
casts sup heal.

My chanter friends love it..   :)

Anyway, that's my roleplay.. Anymore then that, and I would have to say that she is too religious!! lol

Sho

------------------
Shohanna Curesurtales
41st level Cleric
The Unseelie Court

